snippet.title: My Hometown VX  - RPG Maker VX
snippet.description: This is the English translation of Japanease Earthbound-like cell-phone RPGwhose name is "boku no sumu machi(My Home Town, ぼくのすむまち)".The translasion tool is RPG Maker VX(RPG tkool VX).You can download from: http://www.moonwhistle.org/bokuvx/e_index.html
